<h2>3. Tables</h2>

<p>This section applies <i>only</i> to tables published directly within articles. Tables submitted as Supporting Information have fewer requirements. Tables submitted for direct publication should be included at the very end of the article file, not submitted as separate files.</p>
<h3>Table Specifications</h3>
<p>More detailed information is available here.</p>

